<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head><%- include('partials/head', { title: 'Unlisted — Data Broker Removal Service' }) %></head>
<body>
<%- include('partials/nav') %>

<!-- HERO -->
<header class="pt-16 sm:pt-24 pb-16 sm:pb-20">
  <div class="max-w-[1180px] mx-auto px-5 sm:px-8 grid lg:grid-cols-[1.15fr_0.85fr] gap-10 lg:gap-16 items-center">
    <div>
      <div class="eyebrow">DATA BROKER REMOVAL SERVICE</div>
      <h1 class="font-display font-extrabold uppercase leading-[0.96] tracking-tight mt-4 mb-5 text-[clamp(2.5rem,9vw,5.125rem)]">
        Your name<br>doesn't belong<br>
        <span class="relative inline-block">
          on their list.
          <span class="absolute left-[-4px] right-[-4px] top-[48%] h-[0.42em] bg-signal origin-left scale-x-0 animate-redact" style="animation-delay:0.5s"></span>
        </span>
      </h1>
      <p class="text-bone-dim text-base sm:text-lg leading-relaxed max-w-[480px] mb-8">
        Data brokers buy, sell, and republish your home address, phone number, and family details without asking. We track real opt-out requirements for each one and walk you through filing them — automatically where it's actually possible, guided where it isn't.
      </p>
      <div class="flex items-center gap-5 flex-wrap mb-10">
        <a href="/signup" class="btn-primary inline-block">Check my exposure →</a>
        <span class="font-mono text-xs text-steel">30-day money-back guarantee</span>
      </div>
      <div class="flex gap-6 sm:gap-7 flex-wrap font-mono text-xs text-steel">
        <span class="border-l-2 border-line-strong pl-2.5"><%= brokerCount %>+ brokers tracked</span>
        <span class="border-l-2 border-line-strong pl-2.5">Real HIBP breach check</span>
        <span class="border-l-2 border-line-strong pl-2.5">Backed by blockd.ai</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="card p-6 sm:p-7 relative">
      <div class="absolute -top-px right-5 bg-void font-mono text-[10px] tracking-wider text-steel px-2.5 py-1 border border-line border-t-0">CASE FILE</div>
      <div class="flex justify-between items-center py-3.5 pt-1.5 border-b border-line font-mono text-sm">
        <span class="text-steel">NAME</span>
        <span class="relative text-transparent">J. MARTINEZ<span class="absolute inset-y-px -inset-x-1 bg-signal origin-right scale-x-0 animate-redact" style="animation-delay:0.6s"></span></span>
      </div>
      <div class="flex justify-between items-center py-3.5 border-b border-line font-mono text-sm">
        <span class="text-steel">HOME ADDRESS</span>
        <span class="relative text-transparent">412 ELM ST, APT 3<span class="absolute inset-y-px -inset-x-1 bg-signal origin-right scale-x-0 animate-redact" style="animation-delay:0.85s"></span></span>
      </div>
      <div class="flex justify-between items-center py-3.5 border-b border-line font-mono text-sm">
        <span class="text-steel">PHONE</span>
        <span class="relative text-transparent">(203) 555-0142<span class="absolute inset-y-px -inset-x-1 bg-signal origin-right scale-x-0 animate-redact" style="animation-delay:1.1s"></span></span>
      </div>
      <div class="flex justify-between items-center py-3.5 border-b border-line font-mono text-sm">
        <span class="text-steel">EMAIL</span>
        <span class="relative text-transparent">JMARTINEZ@MAIL.COM<span class="absolute inset-y-px -inset-x-1 bg-signal origin-right scale-x-0 animate-redact" style="animation-delay:1.35s"></span></span>
      </div>
      <div class="flex justify-between items-center py-3.5 font-mono text-sm">
        <span class="text-steel">RELATIVES</span>
        <span class="relative text-transparent">3 RECORDS FOUND<span class="absolute inset-y-px -inset-x-1 bg-signal origin-right scale-x-0 animate-redact" style="animation-delay:1.6s"></span></span>
      </div>
      <div class="flex items-center gap-2.5 mt-4 font-mono text-xs text-verified">
        <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-verified shadow-[0_0_0_3px_rgba(63,174,106,0.18)]"></span>
        5 OF 5 FIELDS REMOVED — CASE CLOSED
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</header>

<div class="border-t border-line"></div>

<!-- STAKES -->
<section id="stakes" class="py-16 sm:py-24">
  <div class="max-w-[1180px] mx-auto px-5 sm:px-8">
    <div class="max-w-[680px] mb-12 sm:mb-14">
      <div class="eyebrow">WHY IT MATTERS</div>
      <h2 class="font-display font-extrabold uppercase leading-[1.02] mt-3.5 text-[clamp(1.75rem,5vw,3rem)]">This is what's on file about you, right now.</h2>
      <p class="text-bone-dim text-base leading-relaxed mt-4 max-w-[560px]">People-search sites and data brokers aggregate public records into a profile anyone can buy for a few dollars. It's legal. It's not harmless.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-px bg-line border border-line">
      <div class="bg-void p-7">
        <div class="font-mono text-[11px] text-signal tracking-wide">01 — NUISANCE</div>
        <h3 class="font-display font-extrabold text-xl uppercase mt-3.5 mb-2.5 leading-tight">Everyday noise</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-bone-dim leading-relaxed mb-3.5">Marketers buy your profile and scrape your contact details. Rarely dangerous, always exhausting.</p>
        <ul class="font-mono text-xs text-steel flex flex-col gap-1.5">
          <li>› Spam calls & emails</li><li>› Junk mail</li><li>› Robocalls</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-void p-7">
        <div class="font-mono text-[11px] text-signal tracking-wide">02 — RISK</div>
        <h3 class="font-display font-extrabold text-xl uppercase mt-3.5 mb-2.5 leading-tight">Cybercriminal target</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-bone-dim leading-relaxed mb-3.5">Attackers need your real details to make a scam convincing. Brokers hand it to them.</p>
        <ul class="font-mono text-xs text-steel flex flex-col gap-1.5">
          <li>› Phishing & scams</li><li>› Identity theft</li><li>› Account takeover</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-void p-7">
        <div class="font-mono text-[11px] text-signal tracking-wide">03 — MONEY</div>
        <h3 class="font-display font-extrabold text-xl uppercase mt-3.5 mb-2.5 leading-tight">Financial drag</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-bone-dim leading-relaxed mb-3.5">Risk-data brokers sell your search history and background to insurers, lenders, and employers.</p>
        <ul class="font-mono text-xs text-steel flex flex-col gap-1.5">
          <li>› Higher premiums</li><li>› Loan denials</li><li>› Lost job offers</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-void p-7">
        <div class="font-mono text-[11px] text-signal tracking-wide">04 — SAFETY</div>
        <h3 class="font-display font-extrabold text-xl uppercase mt-3.5 mb-2.5 leading-tight">Physical exposure</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-bone-dim leading-relaxed mb-3.5">People-search sites hand your home address to any stranger with a browser.</p>
        <ul class="font-mono text-xs text-steel flex flex-col gap-1.5">
          <li>› Stalking</li><li>› Doxxing</li><li>› Swatting</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<div class="border-t border-line"></div>

<!-- PROCESS -->
<section id="process" class="py-16 sm:py-24">
  <div class="max-w-[1180px] mx-auto px-5 sm:px-8">
    <div class="max-w-[680px] mb-12 sm:mb-14">
      <div class="eyebrow">HOW IT WORKS</div>
      <h2 class="font-display font-extrabold uppercase leading-[1.02] mt-3.5 text-[clamp(1.75rem,5vw,3rem)]">What's actually automated — and what isn't.</h2>
      <p class="text-bone-dim text-base leading-relaxed mt-4 max-w-[560px]">Most data brokers don't offer an API. Here's exactly how each step works, honestly.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="flex flex-col">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-[50px_1fr] sm:grid-cols-[90px_1fr_1fr] gap-5 sm:gap-8 py-7 border-t border-b border-line items-start">
        <div class="font-mono text-xs text-steel pt-1"><b class="text-signal text-base">01</b></div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="font-display font-extrabold text-xl sm:text-2xl uppercase mb-2">Check breach exposure</h3>
          <p class="text-bone-dim text-sm sm:text-base leading-relaxed">We check your email against Have I Been Pwned's real breach database — a live, third-party API, not a simulation.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="hidden sm:block font-mono text-xs text-steel text-right pt-1.5"><span class="block text-bone text-2xl mb-1">Live</span>HIBP API call</div>
      </div>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-[50px_1fr] sm:grid-cols-[90px_1fr_1fr] gap-5 sm:gap-8 py-7 border-b border-line items-start">
        <div class="font-mono text-xs text-steel pt-1"><b class="text-signal text-base">02</b></div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="font-display font-extrabold text-xl sm:text-2xl uppercase mb-2">Match against tracked brokers</h3>
          <p class="text-bone-dim text-sm sm:text-base leading-relaxed">We maintain a researched database of real brokers and their actual opt-out mechanism — form, email, phone, or the CA state platform.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="hidden sm:block font-mono text-xs text-steel text-right pt-1.5"><span class="block text-bone text-2xl mb-1">20+</span>brokers tracked at launch</div>
      </div>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-[50px_1fr] sm:grid-cols-[90px_1fr_1fr] gap-5 sm:gap-8 py-7 border-b border-line items-start">
        <div class="font-mono text-xs text-steel pt-1"><b class="text-signal text-base">03</b></div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="font-display font-extrabold text-xl sm:text-2xl uppercase mb-2">We generate the legal request</h3>
          <p class="text-bone-dim text-sm sm:text-base leading-relaxed">Every case file includes a CCPA/GDPR-citing deletion request, pre-filled with your details, ready to send or paste into a form.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="hidden sm:block font-mono text-xs text-steel text-right pt-1.5"><span class="block text-bone text-2xl mb-1">Auto</span>text generated per broker</div>
      </div>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-[50px_1fr] sm:grid-cols-[90px_1fr_1fr] gap-5 sm:gap-8 py-7 border-b border-line items-start">
        <div class="font-mono text-xs text-steel pt-1"><b class="text-signal text-base">04</b></div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="font-display font-extrabold text-xl sm:text-2xl uppercase mb-2">Email-based brokers get sent automatically</h3>
          <p class="text-bone-dim text-sm sm:text-base leading-relaxed">For brokers that accept email opt-outs, we send the request from our system on your behalf. Form-based brokers need a click-through — we link straight to the right page with instructions.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="hidden sm:block font-mono text-xs text-steel text-right pt-1.5"><span class="block text-bone text-2xl mb-1">Mixed</span>auto + guided</div>
      </div>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-[50px_1fr] sm:grid-cols-[90px_1fr_1fr] gap-5 sm:gap-8 py-7 border-b border-line items-start">
        <div class="font-mono text-xs text-steel pt-1"><b class="text-signal text-base">05</b></div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="font-display font-extrabold text-xl sm:text-2xl uppercase mb-2">You track every case to closed</h3>
          <p class="text-bone-dim text-sm sm:text-base leading-relaxed">Your dashboard shows status per broker — not started, sent, pending, verified removed — so nothing falls through the cracks.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="hidden sm:block font-mono text-xs text-steel text-right pt-1.5"><span class="block text-bone text-2xl mb-1">Live</span>status dashboard</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<div class="border-t border-line"></div>

<!-- PRICING -->
<section id="pricing" class="py-16 sm:py-24">
  <div class="max-w-[1180px] mx-auto px-5 sm:px-8">
    <div class="max-w-[680px] mb-10">
      <div class="eyebrow">PRICING</div>
      <h2 class="font-display font-extrabold uppercase leading-[1.02] mt-3.5 text-[clamp(1.75rem,5vw,3rem)]">Pick your level of coverage.</h2>
      <p class="text-bone-dim text-base leading-relaxed mt-4">Cancel anytime. Every plan includes our 30-day money-back guarantee.</p>
    </div>
    <%- include('pricing-partial', { standalone: false }) %>
  </div>
</section>

<div class="border-t border-line"></div>

<!-- PROOF -->
<section id="proof" class="py-16 sm:py-24">
  <div class="max-w-[1180px] mx-auto px-5 sm:px-8">
    <div class="max-w-[680px] mb-12">
      <div class="eyebrow">PROOF</div>
      <h2 class="font-display font-extrabold uppercase leading-[1.02] mt-3.5 text-[clamp(1.75rem,5vw,3rem)]">What's real today.</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-3 border border-line">
      <div class="p-8 sm:p-10 border-b sm:border-b-0 sm:border-r border-line">
        <div class="font-mono text-3xl sm:text-[2.75rem] text-bone font-semibold"><%= brokerCount %>+</div>
        <div class="text-sm text-bone-dim mt-2 leading-relaxed">Real data brokers tracked, each with a verified opt-out method and source.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="p-8 sm:p-10 border-b sm:border-b-0 sm:border-r border-line">
        <div class="font-mono text-3xl sm:text-[2.75rem] text-bone font-semibold">Live</div>
        <div class="text-sm text-bone-dim mt-2 leading-relaxed">Breach exposure checks run against the real Have I Been Pwned API, not sample data.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="p-8 sm:p-10">
        <div class="font-mono text-3xl sm:text-[2.75rem] text-bone font-semibold">CA</div>
        <div class="text-sm text-bone-dim mt-2 leading-relaxed">California residents get a direct link to the state-run DROP platform, covering 540+ registered brokers in one request.</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<div class="border-t border-line"></div>

<!-- BLOCKD.AI BANNER -->
<section class="py-16 sm:py-24">
  <div class="max-w-[1180px] mx-auto px-5 sm:px-8">
    <div class="card p-7 sm:p-10 flex flex-col sm:flex-row sm:items-center justify-between gap-6">
      <div class="flex items-start sm:items-center gap-4 sm:gap-5">
        <div class="font-mono font-semibold text-sm bg-void border border-line-strong px-3.5 py-2 text-bone whitespace-nowrap">blockd.ai</div>
        <p class="text-sm text-bone-dim leading-relaxed max-w-[520px]"><b class="text-bone">Unlisted is built in support of blockd.ai's mission</b> — making personal data harder to harvest, trade, and exploit at scale. A share of every subscription helps fund that work.</p>
      </div>
      <a href="#" class="btn-outline whitespace-nowrap">Learn more →</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<div class="border-t border-line"></div>

<!-- FAQ -->
<section id="faq" class="py-16 sm:py-24">
  <div class="max-w-[1180px] mx-auto px-5 sm:px-8">
    <div class="max-w-[680px] mb-12">
      <div class="eyebrow">QUESTIONS</div>
      <h2 class="font-display font-extrabold uppercase leading-[1.02] mt-3.5 text-[clamp(1.75rem,5vw,3rem)]">Before you sign up.</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="faq-list">
      <div class="faq-item border-t border-line">
        <button class="faq-q w-full text-left py-5 flex justify-between items-center gap-4 font-display font-bold text-base sm:text-lg uppercase">
          What is a data broker?<span class="plus font-mono text-signal text-xl transition-transform">+</span>
        </button>
        <div class="faq-a hidden"><p class="text-bone-dim text-sm sm:text-base leading-relaxed pb-5 max-w-[680px]">A company that scrapes the internet and public records for personal information, aggregates it into a profile, and sells that profile to advertisers, insurers, employers, and other data brokers.</p></div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item border-t border-line">
        <button class="faq-q w-full text-left py-5 flex justify-between items-center gap-4 font-display font-bold text-base sm:text-lg uppercase">
          Is the breach check real?<span class="plus font-mono text-signal text-xl transition-transform">+</span>
        </button>
        <div class="faq-a hidden"><p class="text-bone-dim text-sm sm:text-base leading-relaxed pb-5 max-w-[680px]">Yes — it queries the live Have I Been Pwned v3 API server-side. It tells you which known breaches your email has appeared in, which is a real, verifiable signal of exposure.</p></div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item border-t border-line">
        <button class="faq-q w-full text-left py-5 flex justify-between items-center gap-4 font-display font-bold text-base sm:text-lg uppercase">
          Does Unlisted automatically remove me from every broker?<span class="plus font-mono text-signal text-xl transition-transform">+</span>
        </button>
        <div class="faq-a hidden"><p class="text-bone-dim text-sm sm:text-base leading-relaxed pb-5 max-w-[680px]">Honestly: not yet, for every broker. Email-based opt-outs are sent automatically on your behalf. Form-based brokers need a click-through on your end — we generate the exact request text and link you straight to the right page so it takes seconds, not research.</p></div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item border-t border-line">
        <button class="faq-q w-full text-left py-5 flex justify-between items-center gap-4 font-display font-bold text-base sm:text-lg uppercase">
          Why does removal need to repeat?<span class="plus font-mono text-signal text-xl transition-transform">+</span>
        </button>
        <div class="faq-a hidden"><p class="text-bone-dim text-sm sm:text-base leading-relaxed pb-5 max-w-[680px]">Brokers re-scrape the web on their own schedules and will relist you if nothing stops them. Each broker's case file shows a typical reappearance window so you know when to recheck.</p></div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item border-t border-line">
        <button class="faq-q w-full text-left py-5 flex justify-between items-center gap-4 font-display font-bold text-base sm:text-lg uppercase">
          How does this support blockd.ai?<span class="plus font-mono text-signal text-xl transition-transform">+</span>
        </button>
        <div class="faq-a hidden"><p class="text-bone-dim text-sm sm:text-base leading-relaxed pb-5 max-w-[680px]">Unlisted operates in support of blockd.ai's broader work on data exploitation. A portion of subscription revenue goes toward that mission directly.</p></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<div class="border-t border-line"></div>

<section class="py-20 sm:py-28 text-center">
  <div class="max-w-[1180px] mx-auto px-5 sm:px-8">
    <h2 class="font-display font-extrabold uppercase leading-none text-[clamp(2.25rem,9vw,4.25rem)]">Get off the list.</h2>
    <p class="text-bone-dim mt-5 mb-8 max-w-[480px] mx-auto text-base">Start with a real breach check. Cancel anytime, refunded within 30 days if it's not for you.</p>
    <a href="/signup" class="btn-primary inline-block">Check my exposure →</a>
  </div>
</section>

<%- include('partials/footer') %>

<script>
  document.querySelectorAll('.faq-item').forEach(function (item) {
    var btn = item.querySelector('.faq-q');
    var answer = item.querySelector('.faq-a');
    var plus = item.querySelector('.plus');
    btn.addEventListener('click', function () {
      var isOpen = !answer.classList.contains('hidden');
      document.querySelectorAll('.faq-a').forEach(function (a) { a.classList.add('hidden'); });
      document.querySelectorAll('.plus').forEach(function (p) { p.style.transform = 'rotate(0deg)'; });
      if (!isOpen) {
        answer.classList.remove('hidden');
        plus.style.transform = 'rotate(45deg)';
      }
    });
  });
</script>
</body>
</html>
